### Safety &amp; Compliance

The other side of our work is ensuring that everyone using a .eco domain is doing so in line with [.eco's policies](/policies/). For members of our community, we know that your .eco domain name is [integral to your brand](/news/eco-boosts-your-brand/). Our mission is to make sure .eco continues to be recognized as a trusted symbol of sustainability.

We also strive to ensure that the .eco community is protected against various online threats. That's why we warned about risk of [invalid nameservers](/news/security-risk-of-invalid-nameservers/) and we worked with community members to address this issue.

We also wanted to let you know that we are members of the [Internet Watch Foundation](https://www.iwf.org.uk/about-us/), working to make sure that .eco domains are never used to serve <abbr title="Child Sexual Abuse Material">CSAM</abbr>.

