### Climate Action

Climate Action is a key UN Sustainable Development Goal that [we are committed to](https://profiles.eco/bigroom). Publishing [climate reports for every .eco domain](/news/climate-reporting-for-eco-domains/) is one of the steps that we took this year in support of climate action. We also continue to monitor, report on and find new ways to drive down the carbon footprint of running the .eco registry. We've published our [2025 Greenhouse Gas emissions report](/impact/ghg-report-2025/) and are finalizing our carbon neutral certification to ISO 14068.

One new initiative this year is we are working with our domain registrar partners to certify (or recertify) with the [Green Web Foundation](https://www.thegreenwebfoundation.org/) if they run in data centers powered by renewable energy. As we realized in this year's [Eco Web Hosting review](/news/2025-eco-web-hosting-review/), the number of certified hosting providers does not necessarily grow every year. We want to do our part to push more providers to register with the <abbr title="Green Web Foundation">GWF</abbr> and ensure that as many .eco domains as possible are recognized as using sustainable hosting.

